      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. Can you actually write out a couple of paragraphs for the introduction and the first main point? I want it to sound really authoritative, like it's not just \"one way to look at it\" but actually the logical solution to the problem. Try to make the connection between historical policy and current wealth gaps feel unavoidable.",
